<%#
# Hidden Form Partial

This partial renders an input element for number attributes.
By default, the input is a text field.

## Local variables:

- `f`:
  A Rails form generator, used to help create the appropriate input fields.
- `field`:
  An instance of [Administrate::Field::Hidden][1].
  A wrapper around the number pulled from the database.

[1]: http://www.rubydoc.info/gems/administrate/Administrate/Field/Hidden
%>

<div>
  <%= f.hidden_field field.attribute, step: "any" %>
</div>
